msgid "3900:それは、避けなくちゃ……。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:I had to avoid that.[%p]"

msgid "4000:グリムに教えてもらったまとめサイトのアドレスに飛ぶ。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:I went to the address that Grimm gave me.[%p]"

msgid "4100:トップには大きく『ニュージェネまとめ』とそのまんまのタイトルが表示されている。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:The top banner read “NewGen Aggregator” in big letters.[%p]"

msgid "4200:まとめサイトってのは、一例としては[color index="A0FF0000"]Ｗｉｋｉ[color index="800000"]を使って不特定多数の人が特定のネタに関する情報を書き込めるサイトのことを言う。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:Aggregator sites were a kind of [color index="A0FF0000"]wiki[color index="800000"], where any number of people could add information to articles about a certain topic.[%p]"

msgid "4300:ニュージェネのまとめサイトなら、ニュージェネに関する情報をいろんな人が書き込んで随時更新していく。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:A NewGen aggregator site would have information about NewGen, constantly updated by different users.[%p]"

msgid "4400:信憑性の薄い情報も混じってるし、荒らしもいるけど、簡単に事件の全体像を理解するには便利だ。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:Some of that information wasn't trustworthy in the slightest, and sometimes there were trolls, but if you wanted an easy way to get a handle on the basic facts of something, it was good.[%p]"

msgid "4500:リンクもたくさん貼ってあるし。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:There were always tons of links, for one thing.[%p]"

msgid "4600:さっそく、『ここまでの流れ』というのを読んでみる。[linebreak]自然と鼓動が速くなった。まとめサイトを読むだけなのに緊張していた。手の平がじっとりと汗ばむ。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:I decided to start with an article called “The Case So Far.” My pulse started to quicken. Just reading the site was enough to make me nervous. I could feel the sweat forming on my hands.[%p]"

msgid "4700:第１の事件――通称『集団ダイブ』は、高校生の男女５人による集団飛び降り自殺だ。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:The first case, the one they called “Group Dive,” was when a group of five boys and girls from a high school had all jumped off a building.[%p]"

msgid "4800:９月７日――今から約１ヶ月前の深夜、渋谷コーネリアスタワー。[linebreak]屋上のヘリポートから墜落した５人はもちろん即死だった。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:It happened on September 7th, about a month ago. It was in the middle of the night, at a place called Shibuya Cornelius Tower. The five had jumped off the building's helipad and died instantly on impact.[%p]"

msgid "4900:司法解剖の結果、５人それぞれの手の爪には本人以外の肉片が残されており、同時に引っ掻き傷も見つかった。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:The autopsy showed that each of them had DNA belonging to someone else under their nails, and there were scratch marks found, too.[%p]"

msgid "5000:そこから、５人がどうやら手を繋いだまま飛び降りたのだと推測されている。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:It was theorized from this that the five of them must've jumped off while holding hands.[%p]"

msgid "5100:屋上には遺書らしきものはなにもなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:There was no sign of any kind of suicide note left on the roof.[%p]"

msgid "5200:以下はネットの有志（通称[color index="A0FF0000"]スネーク[color index="800000"]）が実際にコーネリアスタワーに行って確かめたことだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:Below the summary was some information added by some internet detective (these types were often referred to as “[color index="A0FF0000"]snakes[color index="800000"]”) who'd actually gone to Cornelius Tower.[%p]"

msgid "5300:屋上は関係者以外立ち入り禁止であり、そこへ通じる扉はほぼ常時、施錠されたままだという。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:According to him, the roof was off limits to visitors, and the door to it was kept locked at all times.[%p]"

msgid "5400:当然ながら事件当時も、鍵はかけられていた。５人の遺品からその扉の鍵は見つからなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:Of course, it was locked at the time of the jump, too. None of the deceased had a key on their bodies when they'd been found.[%p]"

msgid "5500:つまり屋上ヘリポートは事実上“密室”状態であり、５人がどうやって屋上のヘリポートに侵入したのか、一切不明である。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:This meant that the helipad was, in a way, a “locked room,” like you saw in murder mysteries. There was nothing to suggest how the five of them had gotten up there.[%p]"

msgid "5600:もしかすると５人以外の“誰か”が事件当時そこにいた可能性が高い。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:It was entirely likely that someone else had been there as well.[%p]"

msgid "5700:第２の事件――通称『妊娠男』殺人事件は、９月１９日、第１の事件から１２日後に起こった。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:The second case, the “Pregnant Man,” happened on September 19th, around twelve days after the first.[%p]"

msgid "5800:早朝、渋谷駅のガード下付近にて、カラオケ帰りの大学生が、血まみれで倒れている男性を発見した。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:Early in the morning, near a Shibuya Station underpass, a college student was walking home from karaoke when they'd found a bloodstained man collapsed on the ground.[%p]"

msgid "5900:この男性は渋谷区在住の大学生、近衛千鶴男（２１）で、発見されたときにはすでに死亡していたが、腹部が不自然に大きく腫れ上がっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:The collapsed man was a university student who lived in Shibuya Ward named Chizuo Konoe (Age 21). He was dead when he was found, but he had an unnatural bulge in his stomach.[%p]"

msgid "6000:司法解剖したところ、男性は何者かによって腹部を切開され、胃の中に生まれたての胎児を閉じこめたまま縫合されたらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:The autopsy showed that someone had opened up his chest, shoved a newborn baby into his stomach, and then sewn him back up.[%p]"

msgid "6100:なお、ＤＮＡ鑑定によって胎児と被害者に血縁関係はないことが判明している。被害者は独身であり、また交際していた女性もいなかったとのこと。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:In addition, DNA analysis had shown that there was no relation between the baby and the man. He was, according to reports, unmarried and had no girlfriend.[%p]"

msgid "6200:ここからはネット上の憶測になるけど、胎児はだいたい妊娠３２週目ぐらいの状態で、そうだとすると母親の身体から帝王切開をして取り上げられたと思われる。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:The rest of it was internet speculation, but the baby appeared to be in the 32nd week of pregnancy, which would mean it was probably removed from the mother by c-section.[%p]"

msgid "6300:でもその母親がいったい誰なのか、そして今現在どこでなにをしているのか、そもそも生きているのか死んでいるのかについては、一切不明らしい。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:Who the mother was, though, or where she was or what she was doing, or even if she was alive or dead... None of that was known.[%p]"

msgid "6400:警察はもしかすると行方をつかんでるかもしれないけど、少なくとも世間には公表されてない。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:It was possible that the cops knew, but if they did, they weren't talking.[%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]拓巳[line]「うっえ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]拓巳[line]Ugh...[%p]"

msgid "6600:吐きそうになって、僕はモニタから目をそらした。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:I looked away from the monitor, feeling like I was about to throw up.[%p]"

msgid "6700:なんておぞましいんだ……。犯人は絶対に狂ってる。[linebreak]しかも……もしかしたらこの凄惨な殺人を……[%p]"
msgstr "6700:This was disgusting. The killer was insane. I knew that for sure. And... it was also possible...[%p]"

msgid "6800:あの女がやったかもしれないなんて……[%p]"
msgstr "6800:That girl had been behind these horrible murders.[%p]"

msgid "6900:日本ｵﾜﾀ＼(^o^)／[%p]"
msgstr "6900:Welp, Japan's screwed! ＼(^o^)／[%p]"

msgid "7000:星来たんをじっと見つめて、目の保養。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:I took a moment to gaze at my beautiful Seira-tan.[%p]"

msgid "7100:なんとか精神状態を安定させる。先生にもらった薬を飲むことも考えたけど、まだ星来たんだけでなんとかなった。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:Looking at her helped calm me down. I thought about taking the sedatives the doctor had given me, but for now, Seira-tan was good enough.[%p]"

msgid "7200:それでも、ナイトハルトとしての面子を保つためとはいえ、こんなグロいものを読むのはやっぱり辛いよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:Still, though... I had to do it to keep up KnightHeart's reputation as a leader, but reading these... hurt.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]星来[line]「そんなに辛いならさ、読まなくていいってぇ」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]星来[line]If it hurts that much, don't read them![%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]星来[line]「タッキーがドＭってんなら別に止めないけど」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]星来[line]I mean, if you're a masochist, I won't stop you.[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]星来[line]「辛そうなタッキーは見てられないんさ」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]星来[line]But seeing you suffer hurts![%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]星来[line]「もうやめよ？　楽しいことだけしてようよ」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]星来[line]Forget about this. Just do something fun![%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]星来[line]「いつもみたく、あたしにハァハァしてもいいからさ」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]星来[line]You can use me to jerk off like you usually do, if you want![%p]"

msgid "7800:うう、星来たんはなんて優しいんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:Seira-tan was such a nice girl.[%p]"

msgid "7900:僕の味方でいてくれるのは星来たんだけだよ。[linebreak]さすが僕の嫁。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:She was my only true ally. My wife.[%p]"

msgid "8000:テーブルの上に頬杖をついて、僕は深呼吸しつつ星来たんの笑顔を見つめる。はぁ、癒される……。[%p]"
msgstr "8000:I put my elbow on the table and rested my head in my hand, taking deep breaths as I stared at Seira-tan's smile. Whew... I felt so much better.[%p]"

msgid "8100:星来たんをチラ見しつつ読んでいけば、もう少しは耐えられるかもしれない。[linebreak]ということで早速実践してみることにした。[%p]"
msgstr "8100:Maybe I could read a little more if I took breaks to glance over at Seira-tan. I decided to give it a try.[%p]"

msgid "8200:そもそもどうして、関連性がまったくないこのふたつの事件が『ニュージェネ』とひとくくりにされるようになったんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:Why had these two seemingly separate incidents both been given the label New Generation Madness?[%p]"

msgid "8300:『集団ダイブ』は、最初あくまで自殺として扱われたらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:The Group Dive was treated as just a suicide at first.[%p]"

msgid "8400:だけど『妊娠男』事件後に『集団ダイブ』の再検証がネット上で行われて、現場の不自然な状況が発覚し――[%p]"
msgstr "8400:But after the Pregnant Man case, the net started taking another look at the Group Dive, and found out how many strange elements there were to the case.[%p]"

msgid "8500:“５人は自殺に見せかけて殺されたのではないか”との説がささやかれ始めた。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:Speculation began that it was actually a murder, not a suicide.[%p]"

msgid "8600:『集団ダイブ』で亡くなった５人の親たちや、５人をよく知る友人たちも口々に、彼女たちが自殺をするなどあり得ないと語ったらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:Supposedly, the parents of the dead kids, and their friends, all said there was no way they could've killed themselves.[%p]"

msgid "8700:そこに至って、マスコミは事件現場が同じ“渋谷”という点から[%p]"
msgstr "8700:Since both the cases were in Shibuya, a traditional center for young people,[%p]"

msgid "8800:『新世代の若者達が生み出した狂気』[linebreak]『ニュージェネレーションの狂気』[%p]"
msgstr "8800:the news started calling it “The Madness Created by the New Generation of Youth,” and then simply, “The New Generation Madness.”[%p]"

msgid "8900:というセンセーショナルな見出しを使い始めた……ということなんだそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:The name stuck.[%p]"

msgid "9000:そして、第３の事件……。[linebreak]僕が目撃した、通称『張り付け』殺人事件だ。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:And then there was the third case... The “Crucified” murder, they were calling it. That was the one I'd seen.[%p]"

msgid "9100:まとめサイトには、まだ事件発生から日が浅いせいか、それほど多くの情報は出ていなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:The Aggregator site didn't have much information on the case because it was so new.[%p]"

msgid "9200:被害者が太田久という５６歳の大学教授であること、杭で空き家のコンクリート壁に遺体が張り付けにされていたことぐらいしか公表されてないらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:The murdered man was Hisa Ota, a 56-year-old college professor. He'd been nailed with stakes to the concrete wall of an empty house.[%p]"

msgid "9300:現場付近では、犯行が行われたとされる午後８時ぐらいから１時間以上にわたって、“釘を打ち付けるかのような音”を聞いた住民が何人かいるらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Starting at 8:00 PM, the estimated time of the crime, neighbors heard what sounded like “something hammering a nail.” The sound lasted for approximately an hour.[%p]"

msgid "9400:その音は僕も聞いた。今も耳にこびりついている。イヤな音だった。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:I'd heard that sound, too. I could still hear it. It was an awful sound.[%p]"

msgid "9500:ちなみに『集団ダイブ』『妊娠男』いずれとの関連性も今のところ見つかっていない。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:For what it was worth, no connection had been found between it and the Group Dive or the Pregnant Man.[%p]"

msgid "9600:けど、同じ渋谷でこれだけ異常な事件が立て続けに三度も起こったことにより、当然のようにこの『張り付け』殺人事件もニュージェネのひとつとして扱われることになった。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:But after three bizarre incidents in the same city of Shibuya, everyone naturally treated the Crucified murder as the third part of the New Generation Madness.[%p]"

msgid "9700:警察やマスコミでは３つの事件はすべて別々の人間による犯行だと見ているけど――[%p]"
msgstr "9700:The media and police were saying that all three were committed by different individuals, but...[%p]"

msgid "9800:ネットでの論調――というより期待――としては、同一犯、あるいは同一グループによる犯行という説が主流だ。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:The position, or rather hope, of most people online was that it was a single person, or failing that, a single group.[%p]"

msgid "9900:他にはオカルト説なんかもネットではよくささやかれているみたいで、すべての始まりは２ヶ月前の地震に起因するという意見もあった。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:There were some bizarre theories involving the occult going around too, and some people were saying NewGen got its start in the earthquake two months ago.[%p]"

msgid "10000:２ヶ月前、渋谷を震源地にして起きた震度３の地震。[linebreak]規模は大したことがなかったにもかかわらず、[linebreak]８人もの死者が出たって言って話題になったやつだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:Two months ago, there'd been an intensity 3 earthquake in Shibuya. An intensity 3 quake was small enough that you could be walking down the street and not feel it. But despite the small size of the quake, it had made the news because eight people had died.[%p]"

msgid "10100:言われてみれば確かに、ニュージェネ事件が始まったのはその地震以降だ。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:Looking back, it was true that the NewGen incidents had started after the earthquake.[%p]"

msgid "10200:だから“ニュージェネ・オカルト派”は、その地震で８人が亡くなったことこそニュージェネ第１の事件としてカウントすべき、みたいに主張して――[%p]"
msgstr "10200:So, the proponents of the “occult theory” were saying that the eight deaths in the earthquake could be counted as the first NewGen case.[%p]"

msgid "10300:“ニュージェネ・主流派”との間に論争が起きていたりする。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:Sometimes they'd get into arguments with the more “mainstream” NewGen theorists.[%p]"

msgid "10400:いずれにせよ、これだけの凶悪事件が連続で三件も起きたにもかかわらず、すべての事件で犯人の手がかりすら見つけられないというのは異常事態だ。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:No matter who was behind it, it was bizarre that three such incidents could happen without a single clue as to who was behind it.[%p]"

msgid "10500:そしてネットでは、第４の事件を待ち望む声が多い。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:A lot of people online were eagerly awaiting a fourth incident, too.[%p]"

msgid "10600:きっと僕も、当事者じゃなかったらこの“祭り”に参加していたかもしれない。そして第４の事件をワクテカして待っていたかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:If I wasn't directly involved, I might've been all wktk myself, participating in the festival and eagerly waiting for a fourth incident, too.[%p]"

msgid "10700:くそっ、どいつもこいつもいい気なもんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:Damn it. They were all having so much fun when I was feeling miserable.[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]拓巳[line]「犯人を早く捕まえてくれよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]拓巳[line]Why can't you just catch the guy already?[%p]"

msgid "10900:『張り付け』から１週間以上になるけど、あの悪魔女も警察もなんの動きも見せない。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:It'd been over a week since Crucified, and there'd been nothing from the demon girl or the police.[%p]"

msgid "11000:もし僕があの場に居合わせたって知られているなら、少なくとも警察は話を聞きに来るはずだ。でも今のところその気配はない。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:If they knew I was there, at a minimum the police would've come to talk to me. But there was no sign of them.[%p]"

msgid "11100:よ、よかった。[linebreak]僕が巻き込まれることはなさそうだぞ――[%p]"
msgstr "11100:W-Whew... It looked like I was going to be able to stay out of this... to not get involved.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]優愛[line]「あなたには、予知能力がありますか？」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]優愛[line]Can you see the future?[%p]"

msgid "11300:優愛が僕に突きつけた言葉が脳裏をよぎった。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:Yua's words flashed through my mind.[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]優愛[line]「予知能力があるって思わなきゃ、納得できないような画像データを、あなたが持っていたから」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]優愛[line]If you can't see the future, I don't know how to explain how you'd have these images.[%p]"

msgid "11500:安心しかけたのに、一瞬にして鬱な気分に逆戻りしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:Just when I was about to finally relax, I suddenly found myself feeling awful again.[%p]"

msgid "11600:『将軍』から送信されてきた画像。[linebreak]それは今も僕のＰＣの中にデータとして残ってる。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:The photos that Shogun had sent me... They were still stored on my computer.[%p]"

msgid "11700:優愛の言ったことはあいつの妄想でしかないんだ。[linebreak]支離滅裂すぎて推理として破綻してる。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:Everything Yua had said was just a figment of her own delusions. It was crazy. It wasn't even a real theory.[%p]"

msgid "11800:結局今日は病院でそのことについて聞けなかったけど、僕が記憶を失ってる間に別の行動をしてたなんて、そんなのあり得ない。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:I hadn't been able to ask about it at the hospital, but there was no way I could have been someplace else while I was awake, doing something I didn't remember. It was impossible.[%p]"

msgid "11900:今までそんなこと一度もなかったんだし。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:It had never happened before, for one thing.[%p]"

msgid "12000:だからあのグロ画像は、合成に決まってる。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:Those guro photos had to be fake.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]星来[line]「だったらさ――」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]星来[line]If you think they are...[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]星来[line]「合成だって証拠を見つけちゃえばいいんさ」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]星来[line]Then prove it![%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]星来[line]「あの画像、解析しちゃおうよ」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]星来[line]Let's analyze those images![%p]"

msgid "12400:で、でも、気持ち悪いからあんまり見たくないんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:B-But they're creepy, and I don't really want to look at them.[%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]星来[line]「あの女を論破しちゃえば、タッキーはもう怯えることなく平穏な生活に戻れるんだよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "12500:[name]星来[line]If you can prove that they're fake to that woman, you'll be able to go back to your normal life, and have nothing to be afraid of![%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]星来[line]「やるしかないっしょ！」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]星来[line]You've gotta do it![%p]"

msgid "12700:だよね……。その通りだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:Yeah... That's right.[%p]"

msgid "12800:優愛はまるで僕が『張り付け』の犯人であるかのような言い方だったけど、そんなわけがないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Yua seemed convinced that I was the one behind Crucified. But that was impossible.[%p]"

msgid "12900:だって僕自身が、犯人の顔を見てるんだから。[linebreak]罪をなすりつけられてたまるか……。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I'd seen the person who'd actually done it. I couldn't let her blame me for the crime.[%p]"

msgid "13000:僕はゴクリと息を呑むと、画像のキャッシュがあるはずのフォルダをダブルクリックした――[%p]"
msgstr "13000:I gulped and double clicked to open the folder where my cache was stored.[%p]"

